channel.title: Is there any client that works on testscape?
channel.description:
well right now ive added new shops and everything on testscape and it was working all well in moparscape, but now that i added stuff in the shops like pk equipment, it keeps logging me off. So im kinda wondering if theres any client besides moparscape that works on testscape?
Or is there anyway i can make a client out of the testscape source? need help please im new :) ! and yes even though im new i dont like leeching :P i like starting from scratch , and learning my way up :D ! so can anyone help me out?
